title: The Black-Bearded Barbarian
creator: Mary Esther Miller MacGregor
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of The Black-Bearded Barbarian by Mary Esther Miller MacGregor (Marion Keith). Read by Edmund Bloxam A fictionalized biography of George Mackay (1844-1901), an influential Presbyterian missionary in northern Taiwan. (Summary by Edmund Bloxam) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
